{"tid":803662,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴: 依家只係輸左兩場, 已經累積咗3分,仲有35場未踼","createTime":"2018-09-02T12:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T13:03:13.000Z","uid":143608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c5edd6b8164f6153b289b4a070a40f3fe1c0c5","tid":803662,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:28:12.000Z","msg":"摩連奴表示一早估計到曼聯季初表現差<br />\n<br />\n曼聯新季首場贏李斯特城，之後輸給白禮頓及熱刺，特別輸給熱刺0：3令外界大肆抨擊。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴對於現狀感到不滿，但是他承認現時局面是預計之內：「暑假時我已經講過，今季是會很難應付。但我們只是輸了兩場，還有35場聯賽未踢。未來還有很多比賽，也許我們會接連贏回幾仗。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=%2FgdtsKkrcp3hrtS81%2FU87DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d3cf879b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"76295641d7b68e85215457b8e7172bf60c20c647","tid":803662,"uid":111425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"摩佬都有上連登"},{"pid":"a41dcce605f2dc6ae5bebc272680943497e84870","tid":803662,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T13:03:13.000Z","msg":"今季有前四都偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}